comments: Murray (SAS) legally contests Simons' (POR) jump shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Poeltl (SAS) establishes himself in a legal position in Powell's (POR) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Poeltl (SAS) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Powell (POR) moves laterally toward DeRozan (SAS) and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) places his forearm against DeRozan (SAS) and releases from contact as DeRozan's momentum carries him away from the play.
Covington (POR) establishes himself in a legal position in White's (SAS) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Covington (POR) reaches in and makes contact with the ball during Walker IV's (SAS) drive. Covington maintains a legal guarding position during the steal.
White (SAS) makes incidental contact to Powell's (POR) arm following the release of his shot attempt near the rim.
Poeltl (SAS) makes contact with the ball while it is in the cylinder during Powell's (POR) shot attempt near the rim.
Powell (POR) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Jones Jr. (POR) legally contests Gay's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Poeltl (SAS) as he gathers the rebound.
Covington (POR) makes contact to Poeltl's (SAS) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
